Bondi on Windows

INSTALLATION:

Extract the zip file to a directory of choice. eg. c:\bondi
  
USING BONDI ON WINDOWS:

1. Click Start 
2. Click Run... Dialog 
3. type in 'cmd'. This will start windows prompt
4. On the prompt window type 'cd c:\bondi'
5. '.\bondi' you should now have bondi toplevel interpreter



